description:
This is a 10 minute workout called '10 min Kids Cardio Workout - HIIT - 30s/20s Intervals - No equipment' from the channel Group HIIT.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This short but fun workout is perfect for 8-16 year olds that want to get some exercise at home or families that want to work out together. Easy to follow videos;  the only sound is timer beeps. Use Chromecast to cast this video to your TV or stream it on a mobile device while you watch your favorite show.
